blog.description: A fanfiction story of my own creation

title: Poliwhirl
excerpt: Poliwhirl is a frog Pokemon. It is the evolved form of Poliwag. Poliwhirl, when it evolves, the swirl on its stomach changes direction. A Poliwag's swirl goes counter clockwise. It then changes to going clockwise when it evolves. What Poliwhirl evolves into depends on a specific item that is used on it. When a Waterstone is used on it, it evolves into a Poliwrath, a dual Water/Fighting type Pokemon. But when it's holding a King's Rock, it evolves into a Politoed.

title: Poliwag
excerpt: Poliwag is a small tadpole Pokemon. Poliwag comes from a line of amphibious Pokemon. Poliwag starts out with a tail and no arms. It then evolves into a Poliwhirl, in which it becomes frog-like and grows a set of arms. Poliwag starts out young and not very powerful but is very well adapted to living in the water and on land. They can be found in swamp and marsh area.
